Clock set to 72 mhz for fastest data procssing using pll but prepherals set to minmum needed clock for power saving 
Clock Security System is enabled
RTC Enabled
Signals are pinned
FreeRTOS enabled V2(tell why Vs) but non preemptive type so that there no need for critical section handling and the tasks are simple and cooperative
DMA is used 
LED for status
using 5v regulator for modem alongside with 3.3v regulator for mcu for modem protection for its sensitivity, using resistance volltage devider, using PTC
can not use freertos with dynamic heap allocation due to lack of main memeory available for jobs BUT static allocation has more promising results